====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# not [[have]]; there is not; to be without
#: {{zh-x|沒意思|uninteresting|lit=to not have interest}}
#: {{zh-x|已經 沒 了|is already gone; there is already no more}}
#: {{zh-x|沒 錢 沒 工作|to have no money and no job}}
